{"tid":470726,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做一個正字撚","createTime":"2017-11-16T14:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T07:07:35.000Z","uid":118267,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f7ed8f3bac1fe45d475171c7aea069a970d2dde0","tid":470726,"uid":118267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:33:49.000Z","msg":"話說小妹中文系，今個sem reg咗科同廣東話有關嘅科，宜家就黎完sem啦，發覺平時我有好多用字都係錯嘅，所以想同大家分享下我之前錯啲乜。<br />\n如果冇讀呢科我應該一世都唔會知自己之前原來係錯嘅。<br />\n個老師同我地講，正確廣東話越黎越少人識，我地讀中文嘅人唔傳開去，應該就冇人傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後正確嘅廣東話就會慢慢消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗下都覺得好可惜<br />\n所以決定係度開po同大家分享下，順便溫下書，講得唔啱嘅求識嘅巴絲打不吝賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先係個「度」字<br />\n<br />\n我見有好多人打字會打「大概有二三十個人到/島啦」<br />\n<br />\n正字應該係「大概有二三十個人度啦」<br />\n<br />\n因為當個「度」字讀成陰上聲嘅時候，表示對數量/時間不太精確的估計，所以「度」應該係正字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後係「咁」同「噉」嘅分別<br />\n應該係小妹孤陋寡聞，其實之前我未見過有人用個「噉」字，所以上堂聽到嘅時候真係都覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來兩個字意思唔同，發音都唔同。<br />\n「噉」讀「gam2」，解這樣，那樣。<br />\n「咁」讀「gam3」，解這麼，那麼。<br />\n<br />\n舉個例，「你咁叻，你做晒佢囉」，呢度嘅「咁叻」係解「這麼厲害」<br />\n<br />\n「噉嘅大話你都講得出」則係解「這樣的謊言都說得出」<br />\n<br />\n仲有「畀」同「俾」<br />\n我平時打字見人用「比」「俾」「畀」都有，其實「俾」「畀」有唔同意思，唔同情況應該用唔同字。<br />\n<br />\n「畀」係主動嘅情況下使用，eg「我畀埋條命你好唔好！」<br />\n「俾」係被動嘅情況下使用，eg「我尋晚俾人打呀」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多，但我例舉唔晒，希望有其他有興趣嘅巴絲幫手補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d296509f31f954ea2c2932ee595aa1d652e62b","tid":470726,"uid":134958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持正字 廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb91b2607f8c8a24f9f1447325d65d235dda29e","tid":470726,"uid":3502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6cc06bbc451434bd9df10c7fecd26479d072409d","tid":470726,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:10:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b1ea198de9af21780712176c1f722f09d537c1e","tid":470726,"uid":3072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"42ea20a7765a39e8daa16835dfb738e0e8d07794","tid":470726,"uid":27437,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"支持 咁樣出Post討論好過肥絲好多"},{"pid":"f5478fc12231dc911498edaa57797970dbe396bc","tid":470726,"uid":48152,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"騎劫<br />\n甜同肺字而家個個都寫錯<br />\n《說文解字》：「舌」字「从干从口」<br />\n第一筆係一橫而唔係一撇<br />\n另外肺字右邊果個唔係「市」字而係「巿」一筆直落到底 <br />\n巿字讀fat1(忽) 係「肺」一字中用作形聲字作聲符"},{"pid":"0082a79ff3eba348d12201747c245d270bce4491","tid":470726,"uid":132533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"真係完全冇見過第二個噉字。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee766332e41b2b619671ac87959e3b35cb880042","tid":470726,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac93703a032b7d9560aa8445ad41517201624846","tid":470726,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:29:57.000Z","msg":"依家D電腦字係咪同真正嗰隻有出入?"},{"pid":"2ae48c6d45550b5736c64bf5f7c0ff4be4440ca9","tid":470726,"uid":118267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"仲有一個宜家成日俾人撈亂用嘅就係「洗」「使」「駛」<br />\n<br />\n見有人打字會打：洗唔洗錢㗎？/駛唔駛咁惡啊！<br />\n<br />\n小妹認為正字應該係「使」，「使」可以讀成天使個「使」，又可以讀成「sai2」。其中一個解釋係「用」<br />\n<br />\n所以例如呢句「呢樣嘢洗唔洗錢㗎？」，用個「洗」字即係wash the money?<br />\n<br />\n如果用「駛」，解駕駛，亦都解唔通，所以正字應該係「使」，成個句子的意思是：這個東西要用錢（買）嗎？"},{"pid":"e3ea3f631e0ba93b9c27282f759c6f393f391d81","tid":470726,"uid":93987,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:37:49.000Z","msg":"玩同挽？"},{"pid":"20a1581db5d8237d8166beaa54e9f261bb3fc3c0","tid":470726,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"好帖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁個 &quot;比&quot; 字幾時用先啱 ?"},{"pid":"053355028b4893f69746fb715ec396c642da2773","tid":470726,"uid":151808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:48:25.000Z","msg":"高質post, ching好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d33d7226c3e24030978dc7e733bfca271865f25","tid":470726,"uid":2123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:55:11.000Z","msg":"極高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4343d65681f47223f6de9a65e875c106a10f86fe","tid":470726,"uid":37971,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩同挽？</blockquote><br />\n大家成日都以為「玩」只係讀「換」，所以喺打廣東話都會打「挽」<br />\n但其實一字多音，「玩」都可以讀「挽」<br />\n<br />\n例如「玩玩具」其實都可以讀「挽換具」<br />\n駛乜分「玩」「挽」兩字?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反正「挽」其實係錯別字</span>"},{"pid":"458b88e5d0971f7a24125d20848caa34bcd8420b","tid":470726,"uid":56239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好帖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁個 &quot;比&quot; 字幾時用先啱 ?</blockquote><br />\n而家都仲通用嘅用法：<br />\n1. 比較/相比：「比上不足，比下有餘。」(作動詞)   「你比我強。」(作介詞)<br />\n2.媲美：「習種似乎自比為毛X東。」<br />\n3. 比喻<br />\n4. 比賽分數：「港隊輸緊二比一。」"},{"pid":"e1d7882717980554392cca69f47ffad3c1f6dc76","tid":470726,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好帖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁個 &quot;比&quot; 字幾時用先啱 ?</blockquote><br />\n而家都仲通用嘅用法：<br />\n1. 比較/相比：「比上不足，比下有餘。」(作動詞)   「你比我強。」(作介詞)<br />\n2.媲美：「習種似乎自比為毛X東。」<br />\n3. 比喻<br />\n4. 比賽分數：「港隊贏緊二比一。」</blockquote>"},{"pid":"45c560dd408780b0e98e03098df92e21f889caac","tid":470726,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好帖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁個 &quot;比&quot; 字幾時用先啱 ?</blockquote><br />\n而家都仲通用嘅用法：<br />\n1. 比較/相比：「比上不足，比下有餘。」(作動詞)   「你比我強。」(作介詞)<br />\n2.媲美：「習種似乎自比為毛X東。」<br />\n3. 比喻<br />\n4. 比賽分數：「港隊贏緊二比一。」</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n唔該晒巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03848aa8cd1b2d9bed9536e663e3fcccad1a404","tid":470726,"uid":118267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩同挽？</blockquote><br />\n大家成日都以為「玩」只係讀「換」，所以喺打廣東話都會打「挽」<br />\n但其實一字多音，「玩」都可以讀「挽」<br />\n<br />\n例如「玩玩具」其實都可以讀「挽換具」<br />\n駛乜分「玩」「挽」兩字?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">反正「挽」其實係錯別字</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dc91df669056d3897afb0dadaad34aa1de0a2e","tid":470726,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"就嚟定就黎？"},{"pid":"d57d9ef83e6ed932e42b473341ed325eddc1a2ed","tid":470726,"uid":149878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T03:48:30.000Z","msg":"尐係咪真係讀D?<br />\n尐同啲邊個啱？"},{"pid":"dffdaadfd64cb43b24eaa82bab42bc455f9d70eb","tid":470726,"uid":30535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T03:59:37.000Z","msg":"長知識了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直以為噉係標奇立異"},{"pid":"3726e9dfee106f15f6237354a713a9d582fa17c5","tid":470726,"uid":119994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:11:07.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"f161059147a15a8389b2e0c4ec0bf26893fb4dd0","tid":470726,"uid":39876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}